xen: Remove hanging references to CONFIG_XEN_PLATFORM_PCI

In 5fbdc10395cd500d6ff844825a918c4e6f38de37 the XEN_PLATFORM_PCI config
option was removed, but references in header files remained. Clean up
those references.

